Package: r300ya
Title: R Interface to Yandex Servie of retelling texts in thesis with YandexGPT
Version: 0.9
Authors@R: 
    person("Andrey", "Kobzev", email = "kobzev.andrew@gmail.com", 
       role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-6641-3072"))
Description: Allows to automatically generate a short description of Internet pages using artificial intelligence technologies (Retelling). To generate a Retelling, the User must specify the URL of the Internet page whose description he wants to generate. For more information see official documents <https://yandex.ru/legal/300ya_termsofuse/>.
